i": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031618_2205259742957243_4814912224586648800_n.png?_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=l_PmhopjQAUQ7kNvgEEw0qM&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYATX-jNURGuE1o6EOoBbDXY98fOhea3vIwryNoPUaO1pg&oe=672C9041"}, {"file_name": "Screenshot_4.png", "id": "326946172620699", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974853_326946175954032_4895921826098113970_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=jXLcx19yhVoQ7kNvgEEMh4J&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCe7aqF61_8xHLO7oW5qyc9xMAE8rgZHKF1RM6gylqLmg&oe=672CB108"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "Screenshot_1.png", "id": "667537957658372", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982512_667537960991705_1442117798375954928_n.png?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=kT2z-mVySxMQ7kNvgHXdD7E&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDMYwDhHPGVLB4l8HPq7lilrTW3_o2R1Q1Y9kVbVryuVQ&oe=672C9668"}, "display_name": "Bliss - Visual Breathing", "keywords": [], "long_description": "Bliss is a revolutionary new way to practice breathwork in virtual reality.\n\nOur body responds to our breathing. Bliss uses science-backed visual breathing aides to help you relax.\n\nMost people don't realize, but there are simple breathing exercises that can significantly improve your health.\n\nBreathing at a particular rate for extended periods of time can be difficult and boring though. So to make it a more enjoyable experience, we've created beautiful visuals that help guide you through \"Resonant Frequency Breathing\" exercises. We call this Visual Breathing.", "short_description": "Bliss is a revolutionary new way to practice breathwork in virtual reality.\n\nOur body responds to our breathing. Bliss uses science-backed visual breathing aides to help you relax.\n\nVisual breathing guides you to breathe at your resonant frequency, which extensive research